<subSubSection pageId="83" pageNumber="84" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="83.[151,1437,1410,1833]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">
This worldwide family of acalyptrate flies has almost 350 species (
<bibRefCitation author="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Pape, T." box="[890,1151,1447,1473]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" refId="ref350035" refString="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Pape, T. (2020) Systema Dipterorum. Version 2. 7. Available from: http: // www. diptera. org / (accessed 30 August 2020)" type="url" year="2020">Evenhuis &amp; Pape 2020</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[1168,1351,1447,1473]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="337 - 351" refId="ref367995" refString="Rondani, C. (1847 d) Osservazioni sopra parecchie specie di esapodi afidicidi e sui loro nemici [part]. Nuovi Annali delle Scienze Naturali e Rendiconto delle Sessioni della Societa Agraria e dell'Accademia delle Scienze dell'Istituto di Bologna, Series 2, 8, 337 - 351, pl. I." type="journal article" year="1847">Rondani (1847d</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[1361,1432,1447,1473]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="432 - 448" refId="ref368051" refString="Rondani, C., (1848 a) Osservazioni sopra parecchie specie di esapodi afidicidi e sui loro nemici [part]. Nuovi Annali delle Scienze Naturali e Rendiconto delle Sessioni della Societa Agraria e dell'Accademia delle Scienze dell'Istituto di Bologna, Series 2, 8 [1847], 432 - 448." type="journal article" year="1848">1848a</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[151,222,1483,1509]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="209 - 214" refId="ref370415" refString="Rondani, C. (1872 c) Sopra alcuni Muscarii parassiti. Note. Bullettino della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 4 (2), 209 - 214." type="journal article" year="1872">
1872 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[210,222,1483,1509]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="243 - 274" refId="ref370928" refString="Rondani, C. (1875 a) Species italicae ordinis dipterorum (Muscaria Rndn.) collectae et observatae. Stirps XXII Lonchaeinae Rndn. Bullettino della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 6 (4) [1874], 243 - 274." type="journal article" year="1875">c</bibRefCitation>
</bibRefCitation>
, 1875a) described 12 Palaearctic nominal species, nine considered as valid and three as junior synonyms (
<bibRefCitation author="Raspi, A." box="[159,294,1519,1545]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="351 - 367" refId="ref365005" refString="Raspi, A. (1983) Contributi alla conoscenza dei Ditteri Camemiidi. III. Considerazioni sulla Leucopis palumbii Rondani e descrizione di Leucopis gloriae n. sp. Frustula Entomologica, New Series, 6 (19), 351 - 367." type="journal article" year="1983">Raspi 1983</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Tanasijtshuk, V. N." box="[308,518,1519,1545]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" refId="ref376091" refString="Tanasijtshuk, V. N. (1984) Family Chamaemyiidae. In: Soos, A. &amp; Papp, L. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Diptera. Volume 9. Micropezidae - Agromyzidae. Elsevier Science Publishers, Amsterdam &amp; Akademiai Kiado, Budapest, pp. 220 - 232." type="book" year="1984">Tanasijtshuk 1984</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Nartshuk, E. P. &amp; Papp, L. &amp; Raspi, A. &amp; Rivosecchi, L." box="[533,774,1518,1545]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="1 - 8" refId="ref360754" refString="Nartshuk, E. P., Papp, L., Raspi, A. &amp; Rivosecchi, L. (1995) Diptera Nerioidea, Diopsoidea, Lauxanioidea. In: Minelli, A., Ruffo, S. &amp; La Posta, S. (Eds.), Checklist delle specie della fauna italiana. 73. Calderini, Bologna, pp. 1 - 8." type="book chapter" year="1995">
Nartshuk 
<emphasis box="[646,705,1519,1545]" italics="true" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">et al.</emphasis>
1995
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Raspi, A." box="[789,922,1519,1545]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="101 - 108" refId="ref365050" refString="Raspi, A. (2003) On the identity of Leucopis (L.) bursaria and description of a new species: Leucopis (L.) spyrothecae (Diptera Chamaemyiidae). Bollettino della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 135 (2), 101 - 108." type="journal article" year="2003">Raspi 2003</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Raspi, A." box="[936,995,1519,1545]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="249 - 254" refId="ref365100" refString="Raspi, A. (2006) On the identity of Parochthiphila (Euestelia) frontella (Diptera Chamaemyiidae). Bollettino della Societa Entomologia Italiana, 138 (3), 249 - 254." type="journal article" year="2006">2006</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Raspi, A. &amp; Benelli, G." box="[1010,1265,1519,1546]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="199 - 219" refId="ref365136" refString="Raspi, A. &amp; Benelli, G. (2016) On the identity of Leucopis (Diptera Chamaemyiidae) described by Camillo Rondani: a revision of eight silver fly species. Bulletin of Insectology, 69 (2), 199 - 219." type="journal article" year="2016">Raspi &amp; Benelli 2016</bibRefCitation>
) in his “ 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">
Stirps 
<taxonomicName box="[151,296,1555,1581]" class="Insecta" family="Lonchaeidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Lonchaeinae">Lonchaeinae</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
”. The family 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hendel" authorityYear="1910" box="[455,637,1555,1581]" class="Insecta" family="Chamaemyiidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Chamaemyiidae</taxonomicName>
was proposed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Hendel, F." box="[842,1022,1555,1582]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="307 - 313" refId="ref352741" refString="Hendel, F. (1910 b) Uber die Nomenklatur der Acalyptratengattungen nach Th. Beckers Katalog der palaarktischen Dipteren, Bd 4. Wiener Entomologische Zeitung, 29, 307 - 313." type="journal article" year="1910">Hendel (1910b)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[1034,1223,1555,1581]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="321 - 342" refId="ref370445" refString="Rondani, C. (1873 a) Degli insetti parassiti e delle loro vittime. Enumerazione con note [concl.]. Bullettino della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 4 (4) [1872], 321 - 342." type="journal article" year="1873">Rondani (1873a)</bibRefCitation>
also proposed two 
<emphasis box="[151,298,1591,1617]" italics="true" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">
nomina 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Maibach et al." authorityYear="1994" baseAuthorityName="Macquart" baseAuthorityYear="1829" box="[242,298,1591,1617]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Paxillaceae" genus="Melanogaster" kingdom="Fungi" order="Boletales" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="nuda">nuda</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
. In his paper on the Rondani types at 
<collectionCode box="[723,807,1591,1617]" country="Italy" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/xa0v-1feb" name="Museo di Zoologia" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">MZUB</collectionCode>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Morge, G." box="[818,987,1590,1617]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="81 - 92" refId="ref360282" refString="Morge, G. (1959 b) Die &quot; amtliche &quot; Dipteren-Sammlung von Prof. Camillo Rondani. Naturkundliches Jahrbuch der Stadt Linz, 6, 81 - 92." type="journal article" year="1959">Morge (1959b)</bibRefCitation>
listed one name (
<emphasis box="[1187,1344,1591,1617]" italics="true" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">nomen nudum</emphasis>
) that he attributed to Rondani. 
<bibRefCitation author="Morge, G." box="[406,577,1627,1654]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="434 - 437" refId="ref360341" refString="Morge, G. (1962 b) Kopulationsapparat und Legrohr der Typen von Leucopis aphidiperda Rondani, 1847 und Leucopis aphidivora Rondani, 1847 (Diptera: Chamaemyiidae). Beitrage zur Entomologie, 12 (3 - 4), 434 - 437." type="journal article" year="1962">Morge (1962b)</bibRefCitation>
designated a 
<typeStatus box="[733,836,1627,1653]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">lectotype</typeStatus>
for 
<taxonomicName authority="Rondani, 1848" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1848" box="[884,1302,1627,1653]" class="Insecta" family="Chamaemyiidae" genus="Leucopis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aphidiperda">
<emphasis box="[884,1129,1627,1653]" italics="true" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">Leucopis aphidiperda</emphasis>
Rondani, 1848
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Rondani, 1847" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1847" class="Insecta" family="Chamaemyiidae" genus="Leucopis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aphidivora">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">Leucopis aphidivora</emphasis>
Rondani, 
<quantity box="[431,487,1663,1689]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.69138" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" unit="in" value="1847.0">1847</quantity>
</taxonomicName>
in the 
<collectionCode box="[565,650,1663,1689]" country="Italy" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/xa0v-1feb" name="Museo di Zoologia" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">MZUB</collectionCode>
. Alfio Raspi and G. Benelli examined the type material in the 
<collectionCode box="[1351,1432,1663,1689]" country="Italy" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/mvk4-k796" name="Museo Zoologico La Specola, Universita di Firenze" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">MZUF</collectionCode>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Raspi, A." box="[151,289,1699,1725]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="351 - 367" refId="ref365005" refString="Raspi, A. (1983) Contributi alla conoscenza dei Ditteri Camemiidi. III. Considerazioni sulla Leucopis palumbii Rondani e descrizione di Leucopis gloriae n. sp. Frustula Entomologica, New Series, 6 (19), 351 - 367." type="journal article" year="1983">Raspi (1983</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Raspi, A." box="[300,359,1699,1725]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="101 - 108" refId="ref365050" refString="Raspi, A. (2003) On the identity of Leucopis (L.) bursaria and description of a new species: Leucopis (L.) spyrothecae (Diptera Chamaemyiidae). Bollettino della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 135 (2), 101 - 108." type="journal article" year="2003">2003</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Raspi, A." box="[369,427,1699,1726]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="249 - 254" refId="ref365100" refString="Raspi, A. (2006) On the identity of Parochthiphila (Euestelia) frontella (Diptera Chamaemyiidae). Bollettino della Societa Entomologia Italiana, 138 (3), 249 - 254." type="journal article" year="2006">2006</bibRefCitation>
) designated a 
<typeStatus box="[586,689,1699,1725]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">lectotype</typeStatus>
for 
<taxonomicName authority="Rondani, 1848" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1848" box="[733,1111,1699,1725]" class="Insecta" family="Chamaemyiidae" genus="Leucopis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bursaria">
<emphasis box="[733,937,1699,1725]" italics="true" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">Leucopis bursaria</emphasis>
Rondani, 1848
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Rondani, 1872" authorityName=", Rondani" authorityYear="1872" class="Insecta" family="Chamaemyiidae" genus="Leucopis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="palumbii">
<emphasis box="[1121,1328,1699,1725]" italics="true" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">Leucopis palumbii</emphasis>
Rondani, 1872
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Rondani, 1875" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1875" box="[260,655,1734,1761]" genus="Ochtiphila" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" rank="species" species="frontella">
<emphasis box="[260,481,1735,1761]" italics="true" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">Ochtiphila frontella</emphasis>
Rondani, 1875
</taxonomicName>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Raspi, A. &amp; Benelli, G." box="[666,926,1735,1762]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="199 - 219" refId="ref365136" refString="Raspi, A. &amp; Benelli, G. (2016) On the identity of Leucopis (Diptera Chamaemyiidae) described by Camillo Rondani: a revision of eight silver fly species. Bulletin of Insectology, 69 (2), 199 - 219." type="journal article" year="2016">Raspi &amp; Benelli (2016)</bibRefCitation>
designated a 
<typeStatus box="[1077,1180,1735,1761]" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">lectotype</typeStatus>
for 
<taxonomicName authority="Rondani, 1875" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1875" class="Insecta" family="Chamaemyiidae" genus="Leucopis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="armillata">
<emphasis box="[1225,1436,1735,1761]" italics="true" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">Leucopis armillata</emphasis>
Rondani, 1875
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Rondani, 1875" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1875" box="[329,734,1770,1797]" class="Insecta" family="Chamaemyiidae" genus="Leucopis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ballestrerii">
<emphasis box="[329,560,1771,1797]" italics="true" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">Leucopis ballestrerii</emphasis>
Rondani, 1875
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Rondani, 1848" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1848" box="[745,1140,1771,1797]" class="Insecta" family="Chamaemyiidae" genus="Leucopis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="misaphida">
<emphasis box="[745,969,1771,1797]" italics="true" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">Leucopis misaphida</emphasis>
Rondani, 1848
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Rondani, 1848" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1848" class="Insecta" family="Chamaemyiidae" genus="Leucopis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="palliditarsis">
<emphasis box="[1193,1436,1771,1797]" italics="true" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">Leucopis palliditarsis</emphasis>
Rondani, 1848
</taxonomicName>
. The type material is distributed between the 
<collectionCode box="[828,906,1807,1833]" country="Italy" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/mvk4-k796" name="Museo Zoologico La Specola, Universita di Firenze" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">MZUF</collectionCode>
(12) and 
<collectionCode box="[1014,1095,1807,1833]" country="Italy" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/xa0v-1feb" name="Museo di Zoologia" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">MZUB</collectionCode>
(two).
</paragraph>
